=== Cardinal number ===
'''два''' (dva) ''m'', две (dve) ''f''

#[[two]] (2)
#:*Last: [[один]] (1)
#:*Next: [[три]] (3)

*''Usage note: '''''два''' and '''две''''', when in the [[nominative case]], even in compounds (22, 32, 42, etc.), always govern the [[genitive]] '''[[singular]]''' of the noun.''
:два [[мальчик|мальчика]] — ''two boys (lit., two of a boy)''
:[[пятьдесят]] два [[мальчик|мальчика]] — ''fifty-two boys (lit., fifty-two of a boy)''
*''The reason for this is that, originally, '''два''' governed the [[dual]] number, and the old [[nominative]] dual form was the same as the masculine [[genitive]] singular. When the [[dual]] number was lost, the form came to be considered the genitive singular which it resembled. This was extended to include the numbers ''[[три]]'' and ''[[четыре]]'', and eventually it applied to feminine nouns as well.''
:две [[книга|книги]] — ''two books (lit., two of a book)''
:[[пятьдесят]] две [[книга|книги]] — ''fifty-two books (lit., fifty-two of a book)''

